24-06-29T21:13:30Z\u0022 title=\u002206/29/2024 09:13  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jun 29\u0022\u003EJune 29\u003C/time\u003E by The Space Peacock\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dandoesstuff","CreatedById":223454,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-06-29T21:18:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRIP\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Krzysztof Jaromir","CreatedById":226446,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-06-29T21:19:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\no7\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PDCWolf","CreatedById":58026,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-06-29T21:21:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt kinda goes to show that some of the issues were very foundational, very few of those bugs require complicated reproduction steps, or are hidden under any sort of depth, yet they\u0027re very persistent or outright unfixable (like the first) without big reworks/redesign. Others are just... bad choices like the maneuver node one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTL;DR reads more like a list of reasons for what happened to the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DibzNr","CreatedById":212219,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-06-29T21:27:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s been fun\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"theJesuit","CreatedById":122369,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-06-29T21:46:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for posting!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RileyHef","CreatedById":228846,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-06-29T21:54:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReally shows what a mess we are now left with.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have heard some people voice their preference towards KSP2 over KSP and, while everyone has their reasoning, this report is a a great indicator why I won\u0027t ever consider seriously playing the sequel again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-06-29T22:54:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean... like half of these were reportedly fixed in the latest patch, were they not?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh yeah I just read the note.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-06-29T22:58:20Z\u0022 title=\u002206/29/2024 10:58  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jun 29\u0022\u003EJune 29\u003C/time\u003E by The Aziz\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Space Peacock","CreatedById":224498,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-03T02:35:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224402720\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022225266\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221719698052\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022228846\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RileyHef\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/29/2024 at 11:54 PM, RileyHef said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have heard some people voice their preference towards KSP2 over KSP and, while everyone has their reasoning, this report is a a great indicator why I won\u0027t ever consider seriously playing the sequel again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSuprisingly, despite seeing pretty much all the bugs this game has during my time as a bug hunter, I am one of those people. Just hit 2000 hours in KSP2 today. Fully understandable that not everybody wants to play a game where dealing with bugs is a necessity though, especially if they consider it to not have many improvements over the original already.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}